Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:03:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New \NWorld, the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After landing on Punk Hazard; an island with \Ntwo parts, one burning, the other frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they learned about the hideous experiments \Nperformed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed off to investigate \Nbut as things got going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they came to form an alliance with the \NHeart Pirates led by Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffy finally encountered Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Samurai Who Can Cut \NFire! Foxfire Kin'emon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:05:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that he had no idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't trust Caesar, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he was being careful \Nand sent an undercover agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet is that agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Warlord-sama now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just arrived. Luckily, I was at Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a ride in an SAD tanker \Nthat was about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I cause any harm to you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No but if you did, you'd be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool grown-ups, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should just finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vergo-san to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:41.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE LABORATORY LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vice Admiral Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I saw him \Nget taken down twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of the Straw Hats got beaten, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Conqueror's Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There can't be that much \Ndifference in their strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was it?! He beat all of \Nthem without even touching them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right, Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what our savior \N- Master is capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! Master! Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strong soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie these five up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Sea Prism Stone chains \Nfor the Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the Navy soldiers here \Nand get inside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange is raining \Ndown but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect this place where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Cool Brothers blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting against Straw Hat and Law \Nmust've been too much for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:42.59,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MIDDLE LAKE - ZORO'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Brook. Convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of negotiation skill is \Ngoing to work for these monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're merging into one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, they're merging into one \Nanother and getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It got bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have a choice? It's my personal mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sanji, I'm a man! I've got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about the Slimes behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass! That worthless chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Don't... Don't attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big, it's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you better not do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, don't! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gas! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes, my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't have eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jelly-ish body entity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison gas, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Zoro-san?! \NIt's poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the same thing before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn from observation, skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the samurai's torso?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Let's use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, they're jellies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you eat and digest them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop talking to me like a bully?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like 70 years older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call "grandpa"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a lively skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai-san?! T-T-Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the Slime's toxin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, I hope his torso \Nis not engulfed by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been using Observation \NHaki for quite a while
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe the torso's getting weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't distinguish its life \Nforce from that of the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you shithead! Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop chewing on it, shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It doesn't hurt at all! It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts... Not really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened to Sanji-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool, let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joue Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I got the last piece safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai puzzle will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison got this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! It's all around me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do it with Nami-san's strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna put a strain on her body again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole lake is turning \Nto the color of the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:15:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't close up! Don't \Nclose up! Don't close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never felt so happy \Nto just have my own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SAMURAI FROM THE WANO \NKINGDOM FOXFIRE KIN'EMON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know you were so tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as tall as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes! Excuse me for not \Nintroducing myself sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in Kuri, Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it already! I'm \Ngonna freeze to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coat will disappear once \Nhe takes it off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny-eyebrow man, what is \Nyour honorable name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the "sir" crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have your whole body back \Nso you've changed your attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were insulting me so much earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hiding behind the fact you were disabled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not forgetting what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you people are barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like pirates! You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't irritate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask me to find your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna owe anything to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't ask you even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm not even capable of \Nfighting back if someone hits me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can carry me if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget your kindness \Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please forgive me for \Nhaving doubts about you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...until I got my torso back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, fool! Lift your head up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men shouldn't kneel on \Nthe ground that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you, sir, weren't there, I probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry to interrupt \Nyou but, Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:40.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE THIRD LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could find out \Nhow he made the drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! It's a book about drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I gotta look for sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the airship is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for them to have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Straw Hat and the others in a \Ncage and carry it to my chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Didn't I tell you \Nto do something about them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped because \Nwe couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such children, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cause any damage to Nami-san's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This body, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna return it, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we burn them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me Foxfire Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can burn and slice an enemy with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me burn them down and \Nclear the way to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can burn and slice an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I cleared the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you, Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were engulfed by \Nthe fire from the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-Kin'emon-san? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just cut the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Foxfire Style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allows me to cut something \Nwith fire and then cut flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no flame that I can't cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm going to go to the \Nlaboratory to save Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm intrigued by a samurai's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you to rescue your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious man suddenly appears \Nand hurts Law with his immense power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His identity causes quite the shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the identity of the powerful \Nenemy that stands behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar and the mysterious \Nman finally comes to light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shocking! The True Identity \Nof the Mystery Man Vergo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
